{"tid":476683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【自吹自擂】被質疑QS排名造假後  「城大校友」登報賣廣告讚母校排名","createTime":"2017-11-22T08:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T09:09:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5eeb8ce2a6b5926ecb337d073d69f50a72a003c1","tid":476683,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171122/s00002/1511288058825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171122%2Fs00002%2F1511288058825&d=iZ8SjhuwUcEPij6oaX2b4J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e0f26f4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171122%2Fs00002%2F1511288058825&h=43e201f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171122/s00002/1511288058825</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171122/s00046/bdd64159eacf0c3b5829d174b25dbe20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171122%2Fs00046%2Fbdd64159eacf0c3b5829d174b25dbe20.jpg&h=135db1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】城市大學呢排被質疑向排名機構QS報細數以改善師生比，令排名更前；自稱為「一群默默支持城大的校友」噚日就喺幾份報紙落廣告，題為「讓我們一起了解出類拔萃的香港城市大學」，仲列咗啲大家未必好熟悉嘅排名榜出嚟，文中隻字不提「報細數」風波。<br />\n<br />\n就呢個風波，城大之前話會交畀四大會計師樓之一核數，校董會主席胡曉明噚日話喺幾個星期後會有結果。<br />\n<br />\n城大校友噚日喺幾份報紙登全版廣告，列出由較少傳媒引述嘅US News &amp; World Report、The UTD Top 100 Business School Research Rankings等機構發表嘅排名，仲話該校唔少學科排全港第一，如生物醫學工程、新聞傳播學、冶金工程等。至於可靠度，就由讀者判斷。"},{"pid":"44a869e3567017b7a4f6b53c273944a6e4aef541","tid":476683,"uid":87506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:28:49.000Z","msg":"一地都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f4e64400b720b0ffa3059387b1f75dacce0ac8","tid":476683,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"而家啲報紙佬幾易做, 用廣東話寫文章都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523660bae67f5115a32b6bceca552b80e97e6889","tid":476683,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"無恥既頂點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738f08362ea4db87fbdc8c1e113255ee658201c9","tid":476683,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.bottle01.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/1018490005464_L1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bottle01.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F1018490005464_L1.jpg&h=12f0cd76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e00ddf867cf91b887bcba158eccfcf56d892ac6","tid":476683,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"下次世界第一<br />\n<br />\n火影世界第一<br />\nCity世界第一"},{"pid":"d22b870bd94fd08c97d15501b4e88d5cea86fc89","tid":476683,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家啲報紙佬幾易做, 用廣東話寫文章都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又話本土<br />\n你想點"},{"pid":"6a65d1eae46edd886ce6ca233ff2737fe16b3461","tid":476683,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"登四張報要成七八十萬起碼"}]}